dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Logan Gonzalez and I will be assisting you today. May I please have your name?
Hello, my name is Amber Coleman.
Great to meet you, Amber! Before we proceed, could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is zero zero three two five.
Thank you, Amber. And for security purposes, can you verify the primary driver's date of birth on the policy?
The primary driver's date of birth is one two three one nineteen ninety-five.
Thank you for confirming, Amber. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about or update regarding your policy today?
I'm looking to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, we can assist you with that. Please provide the make, model, and year of the vehicle you'd like to add.
Thank you for your time, Amber. If you have any further questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
